Class MainFormController

java.lang.Object

Controller.MainFormController

javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget, javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class MainFormController extends javafx.scene.Parent implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
controller class for the main form. handles actions for the parts and products panes. allows users to add, modify, delete, and search for products and parts.
